{"ID":"20260415114902-61hy1kr","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260415114902-61hy1kr","title":"未命名","type":"doc","updated":"20260415115116"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260415115116-ghgl8r4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260415115116-ghgl8r4","updated":"20260415115116"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"好，我们从"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"第五阶段：抽象层次与建模能力"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"开始。"}]},{"ID":"20260415115116-3u20ftx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260415115116-3u20ftx","updated":"20260415115116"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这一阶段最重要的，不是背定义，而是建立一个意识："}]},{"ID":"20260415115116-1jpzz29","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260415115116-1jpzz29","updated":"20260415115116"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"同一个电路功能，可以站在不同“高度”去描述。"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\n你站得越高，越像在讲“它要做什么”；\n你站得越低，越像在讲“它到底由什么门、什么连线组成”。\n原书把 Verilog 模型分成五个抽象级别：​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"系统级、算法级、RTL 级、门级、开关级"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​，并强调一个复杂系统通常由多个模块、多个子模块构成，其中有些要综合成电路，有些只是测试激励或外部环境模型。"}]},{"ID":"20260415115116-7bysnu7","Type":"NodeThematicBreak","Properties":{"id":"20260415115116-7bysnu7","updated":"20260415115116"}},{"ID":"20260415115116-53pz1jq","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260415115116-53pz1jq","updated":"20260415115116"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第五阶段 第 1 课"}]},{"ID":"20260415115116-v6d1rck","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260415115116-v6d1rck","updated":"20260415115116"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Verilog 的五种抽象层次，到底在讲什么"}]},{"ID":"20260415115116-0r1y3fr","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260415115116-0r1y3fr","updated":"20260415115116"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1. 先抓本质"}]},{"ID":"20260415115116-m484bd3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260415115116-m484bd3","updated":"20260415115116"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"你先把这句话记住："}]},{"ID":"20260415115116-nidasmt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260415115116-nidasmt","updated":"20260415115116"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"抽象层次 \\= 你用什么视角描述硬件。"}]},{"ID":"20260415115116-y7b8hqs","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260415115116-y7b8hqs","updated":"20260415115116"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"比如你要描述一个“8 位加法器”。"}]},{"ID":"20260415115116-y3qjvld","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260415115116-y3qjvld","updated":"20260415115116"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"你可以这样说："}]},{"ID":"20260415115116-v0bxsy5","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260415115116-v0bxsy5","updated":"20260415115116"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"说法 A：只说功能"}]},{"ID":"20260415115116-hn6vqfb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260415115116-hn6vqfb","updated":"20260415115116"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“输入 a 和 b，输出 sum "},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"="}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" a + b。”"}]},{"ID":"20260415115116-o4nkrjr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260415115116-o4nkrjr","updated":"20260415115116"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这叫站得高，偏​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"算法级 / RTL 级"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​。"}]},{"ID":"20260415115116-nr6u7dq","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260415115116-nr6u7dq","updated":"20260415115116"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"说法 B：说内部结构"}]},{"ID":"20260415115116-21hl7qi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260415115116-21hl7qi","updated":"20260415115116"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“它由 8 个全加器串起来，低位进位送到高位。”"}]},{"ID":"20260415115116-vxxljn8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260415115116-vxxljn8","updated":"20260415115116"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这叫站得低，偏​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"门级 / 结构级"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​。"}]},{"ID":"20260415115116-aru44p7","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260415115116-aru44p7","updated":"20260415115116"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"说法 C：继续往下"}]},{"ID":"20260415115116-bdfqvze","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260415115116-bdfqvze","updated":"20260415115116"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“每个全加器内部由 xor、and、or 门组成。”"}]},{"ID":"20260415115116-jbd4q5s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260415115116-jbd4q5s","updated":"20260415115116"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这就更低了，接近​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"门级"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​。"}]},{"ID":"20260415115116-nrnr7gz","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260415115116-nrnr7gz","updated":"20260415115116"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"说法 D：再往下"}]},{"ID":"20260415115116-m6zw5gt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260415115116-m6zw5gt","updated":"20260415115116"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“某个门内部由 MOS 管怎么搭。”"}]},{"ID":"20260415115116-5ul023n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260415115116-5ul023n","updated":"20260415115116"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这就是"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"开关级"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"了。"}]},{"ID":"20260415115116-b4fj2dv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260415115116-b4fj2dv","updated":"20260415115116"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"你会发现："}]},{"ID":"20260415115116-0mmy9fo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260415115116-0mmy9fo","updated":"20260415115116"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"功能没变，描述的细节层次变了。"}]},{"ID":"20260415115116-phciywz","Type":"NodeThematicBreak","Properties":{"id":"20260415115116-phciywz"